{"tid":1217072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(支那豬)瑞銀首席經濟學家報告　疑似出現辱華言論","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:05:03.000Z","uid":19552,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de3092f83af49d48ebb43dc8e537a3e6d0cd1bb5","tid":1217072,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"保羅&middot;多諾萬（Paul Donovan）的這份報告中，正文部分依次列舉了美﹑中﹑日三國的通脹情況。第一段寫美國通脹是很正常的情況；第三段日本的通脹情況則是通過機床產量的角度來寫的。<br />\n而在文章中間關於中國的部分，首先指出中國的通脹都是由豬瘟引起的，接下來自問自答：有關係嗎？「如果你是頭中國豬的話就有關係了」（It matters if you are a Chinese pig）。<br />\n瑞銀表示，「需要明確的是，這一評論是關於豬肉價格上漲帶來的通脹和中國消費者價格上升。」瑞銀稱，已經刪除了相關音頻評論。瑞銀網站也刪除了該份報告。<br />\n此外，瑞銀的公關部門還透露，稍後保羅&middot;多諾萬會錄一段道歉的音頻。<br />\n多諾萬是瑞銀全球財富管理公司的首席經濟學家，根據他的LinkedIn頁面，他負責預測並解釋關鍵的經濟趨勢。他已在瑞銀供職超過26年。"},{"pid":"ebeb87e2b972e4807bf2abd14c08d4c6f730ee18","tid":1217072,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2909667/org/898af426226954beda94de8700323722.jpg/aILPpIc134MIE3IRt2EmtTIDWQ05PiCpo3sQ6qN7EOo?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2909667%2Forg%2F898af426226954beda94de8700323722.jpg%2FaILPpIc134MIE3IRt2EmtTIDWQ05PiCpo3sQ6qN7EOo%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=8be8b6bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce4fe23068c85838bf112f076e20f5e2beb124ef","tid":1217072,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654d1d9278cfd653f49a3f586ad484d75b72809a","tid":1217072,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"希望佢冇事<br />\n瑞銀呢間野奶共到仆街"},{"pid":"8ef7e14f9d63fb7125669352d30574551de80e73","tid":1217072,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img